{
  "stem": "8947.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A-- a typical-- you know-- you know how-- how we Jewish people are.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were some entrepreneurs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, interestingly enough, wherever you put the Jews, you know, there is some little business, tradings.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You trade in this, you get this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some people, I don't know what, they had something that the others didn't have. you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and-- so-- so by then-- then-- then there were, you know, some rabbis in the ghetto, you know, who tried to do something. you know?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To-- We tried to give, kind of, strength to each other.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was not-- we were-- we were practically prisoners there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We couldn't get out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "See?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were surrounded by guards.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And [? that's why ?] [? we ?] [? were ?] [? there. ?] And the-- the worst part was, I think-- see I-- I-- that-- that we-- we didn't-- we didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We couldn't do much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We couldn't do much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was nothing to do.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a temporary waiting for something much better.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And look what we got.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were some girls who were from my city, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I even had a schoolmate there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah, some-- I had.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and your question is why didn't I have before-- I answer your, now, question-- more, maybe friends, you were asking me, and in school?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because we-- we Jewish students, we stuck together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we were-- we were persecuted, discriminated, and shunned.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's the truth.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were shunned from the others.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So inside the ghetto, the friends that you had, were you able to get together and talk at all about--",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, we could talk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We could-- that's one thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, we were talking about the good times.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
